column5: to the first person who tells me what dates it is on!!  Only reply if you can go, as tickets will be picked up at the will-call booth.
Now get back to work!! LOL
Saweeeeeeeet!!!!!   Okay, yes, back to work, ahem!!   Thanks hon!
CONGRATS!!! I guess this means you're taking Paul, eh?
Can I have Pauls ticket if I ride a bike up their with 2 flats???   Art
Dammit... I meant ONE free ticket!!!
Joey, start the thread "Bad Contest Experiences"
